Adding font-awesome to your foundatio site


HowTo: Foundation 6 Font Awesome and other asset fonts



bower install fontawesome --save


 Modify 
config.yml


  assets:
    - "src/assets/**/*"
    - "!src/assets/{img,js,scss,fonts}/**/*"
  fonts:
    - "src/assets/fonts/*"
    - "bower_components/font-awesome/fonts/*"
